              "• Select 'Random' to swap whoever is closest, or pick a specific player.\n" ..
              "• Set the amount of times you wish to loop the troll.\n" ..
              "• Enter the arena and turn on 'Swapper Trolling' to begin.\n" ..
              "• Once the script is finished you will be reset to prevent bans.\n" ..
              "• The script stops when you finish or return to the lobby."
})

